{"tid":1677204,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪列治感覺無左以前咁「天下無敵」","createTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:18:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebd080219061e50d4f57a3b7023843484e3695e","tid":1677204,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】祖雲達斯中堅迪列治表示，轉會後感覺沒以前那樣「無敵」。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭國腳迪列治（Matthijs de Ligt）去季成功上位，一度成為巴塞隆拿和巴黎聖日耳門的目標，夏天終由阿積士改投祖雲達斯，身價達到8500萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n可是，登陸意甲似乎「水土不服」，迪列治仍未回復昔日水平，日前接受《霍士體育》訪問時直言：「效力阿積士期間，我覺得天下無敵，但今時不同往日。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為這是無可厚非，因為來到新環境，一切都是新事物，我正不斷進步，對未來毫不擔心。」迪列治至今上陣7場，仍未給人足夠信心，「我也不知道為何發揮未如理想，唯一能做的是，盡力工作，向隊友學習，只要可以繼續落場，我相信慢慢會漸入佳境，我認為這不是體能上的問題。」"},{"pid":"d7bad40568f4230c218e8b485aca63ec48134d09","tid":1677204,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf9702b4514a78c7479a5d4670929cd5b21a023","tid":1677204,"uid":299179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"球球都係輸佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5927988f501b6cd109ec02c2b93dbad19eeda1","tid":1677204,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf9702b4514a78c7479a5d4670929cd5b21a023","tid":1677204,"uid":299179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"球球都係輸佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"C朗傾返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e60c369e74342c0b02ee7ab4f4dadebb63bf05","tid":1677204,"uid":1354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5927988f501b6cd109ec02c2b93dbad19eeda1","tid":1677204,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf9702